OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,FScientists are working on a way to
OL,7,Fmake one of Britain's favourite snacks
OL,8,Fhealthier without ruining their
OL,9,Fdistinctive flaky pastry.
OL,11,FAn estimated 10-15 million sausage
OL,12,Frolls are sold in the UK each week `
OL,13,Fbut a single one can contain more than
OL,14,F60% of an adult's recommended daily
OL,15,Fsaturated fat intake.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
