FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,FNow researchers at Heriot-Watt
OL,7,FUniversity in Edinburgh are developing
OL,8,Fa new way to make their layered
OL,9,Fpastry, saying this could
OL,10,F"significantly" cut the amount of
OL,11,Fsaturated fat.
OL,13,FIf it works, the team said the process
OL,14,Fcould be applied to a range of popular
OL,15,Fpastries to make them healthier.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,FProfessor Stephen Euston, from Heriot-
OL,7,FWatt's School of Engineering and
OL,8,FPhysical Sciences, said: "We want to
OL,9,Flower the level of saturated fat while
OL,10,Fkeeping the taste and texture that
OL,11,Fpeople love.
OL,13,F"We're focused on sausage rolls, but
OL,14,Fthis also applies to other baked goods
OL,15,Fthat contain laminated pastry such as
OL,16,Fcroissants, Danish pastries and sweet
OL,17,For savoury turnovers.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,F"Reducing the saturated fat content of
OL,7,Fthese ubiquitous snacks could have a
OL,8,Fvery positive impact on the nation's
OL,9,Fhealth and waistlines."
OL,11,FThe puff pastry used in sausage rolls
OL,12,Fand other baked goods relies on fat
OL,13,Ffor its distinctive flaky texture.
OL,15,FThe team is hoping to find a way to
OL,16,Freplace the solid fats currently used
OL,17,Fwith healthier liquid oils like
OL,18,Fsunflower or rapeseed, which are lower
OL,19,Fin saturated fat.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,FThis involves using a process called
OL,7,Foleogelation to turn them into a
OL,8,F"solid-like fat".
OL,10,FThe team hopes this will mimic the
OL,11,Fbehaviour of traditional fats, and
OL,12,Fdeliver the same flaky texture.
OL,14,F"Making flaky pastry is surprisingly
OL,15,Fcomplicated," Prof Euston explained.
OL,17,F"The fat is not just there for
OL,18,Fflavour; it plays a crucial structural
OL,19,Frole in the pastry.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]vD@AOUwD@MO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,F"You need the fat sitting between the
OL,7,Flayers of dough so that when the
OL,8,Fpastry bakes, steam forces those
OL,9,Flayers apart and gives you that flaky
OL,10,Ftexture people expect.
OL,12,F"Simply replacing the fat with a
OL,13,Fhealthier oil doesn't work, because
OL,14,Fliquid oils lack the structure needed
OL,15,Fto separate the pastry layers."
OL,17,FThe team said they are focusing on
OL,18,Foils from crops that can be grown in
OL,19,Fthe UK, in order to minimise the
OL,20,Fimpact of the approach on the
OL,21,Fenvironment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,FAs well as potential health benefits,
OL,7,FProfessor Euston said the research
OL,8,Fcould benefit bakers as well.
OL,10,FTraditional laminated pastry often has
OL,11,Fto be chilled repeatedly during
OL,12,Fproduction so that the fat layers do
OL,13,Fnot melt as the dough is folded.
OL,15,FProf Euston said: "We are hoping our
OL,16,Foleogels will stay stable at higher
OL,17,Ftemperatures, which means
OL,18,Fmanufacturers may not have to chill
OL,19,Fthe pastry as much.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,F"If we are lucky, they might not need
OL,7,Fto chill it at all."
OL,9,FThe 10-month project is seeing
OL,10,Fresearchers at Heriot-Watt working
OL,11,Fwith industry collaborators New Food
OL,12,FInnovation and AB Mauri.
OL,14,FThe team has been funded by the UK
OL,15,FResearch and Innovation Engineering
OL,16,Fand Physical Sciences Research Council
OL,17,F(UKRI EPSRC), with the aim of moving
OL,18,Ftheir modified pastry from the lab
OL,19,Finto the kitchen, and putting its
OL,20,Ftaste to the test with real people.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
