PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,FDr Andrew Bourne, UKRI ESPRC's
OL,7,Fexecutive director for innovation and
OL,8,Fpartnerships, said: "UKRI EPSRC's
OL,9,FImpact Acceleration Awards use public
OL,10,Ffunding to turn promising research
OL,11,Finto practical solutions, and this
OL,12,Fproject does exactly that.
OL,14,F"By taking innovative food science out
OL,15,Fof the lab into the kitchen and
OL,16,Ftesting it with everyday consumers, it
OL,17,Fhas the potential to make the nation's
OL,18,Ffavourite snacks healthier and make a
OL,19,Fgenuine difference to our health and
OL,20,Fwellbeing."
OL,26,@pD@UOUvD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
