OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782688690
OL,3,CScientists bid to make sausage rolls
OL,4,Chealthier without ruining flaky pastry
OL,6,FAlongside pastry, the researchers are
OL,7,Falso exploring whether the same
OL,8,Ftechnology could reduce saturated fat
OL,9,Fin vegan cheese alternatives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
